Interface BlenderMorse

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Platform, RoboticSimulator, System
All Known Implementing Classes:
BlenderMorseImpl
public interface BlenderMorse
extends RoboticSimulator

A representation of the model object 'Blender Morse'.

The following features are supported:

  • Debug Mode
  • Debug Display
  • Gravity
  • viewport shade
